data.description: Welcome home to this beautifully updated 7 acre farmette in Hershey! This brick ranch home is exceptionally spacious with updated open floor plan, and newly finished upstairs for additional living space and 3rd bedroom adds a ton of finished square footage to the home. Updated kitchen, bathroom, fresh floors and paint throughout, the updates are endless and nearly everything in the home is less than 5 years old, including the windows. On top of that, the roof is only a few years old and water heater is new. Step out back take notice of the new septic system that was entirely replaced 4 years ago.  As you explore the 7 acre lot, take note that some of the acreage is wooded toward the rear of the property, beyond the field. The bank barn provides tons of endless possibilities for uses, and has water and electric. The electric fence below is handy for animals. Extra low taxes due to Farmstead/Homestead Exemption! This is your rare opportunity to own a large plot of land with a beautifully updated home and huge bank barn, don't let it pass you by! Parking is off of High Drive, along the side of the barn.
